The subject property is a "once in a lifetime" opportunity which is sure to excite every investor, developer and owner occupier across the country!

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: UNIQUE SMALL FITTED SUITE IN LANDMARK OFFICE TOWER

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer Part Level 21 (698sqm), 40 City Road Southgate, featuring a high quality existing fitout comprising circa 70 x workstations, impressive large kitchen/breakout area, 4 x small meeting rooms and a large boardroom.

40 City Road (HWT Tower), enjoys a location that takes in views of the Yarra River, and allows those working there to also take in the delights of this highly regarded dining, arts and retail district. 

Recent works to the tower include brand new, state of the art end-of-trip facilities including showers, change facilities and bike racking, along with walking and cycling tracks that practically go past the front of the building making it a desirable location for budding cyclists, runners and gym-goers. 

With Flinders Street Station and Swanston Street's trams in plain sight from the building's large windows, the benefits of accessibility of the building's position are clear to see. And with a City Road location and St Kilda Road just around the corner, accessing CityLink, Bayside and South Eastern suburbs are a breeze. 

Outside your door are countless opportunities for entertaining clients, having a lunch time stroll in a park or riverside, and Crown Casino and South Wharf are just a short brisk walk away as well.
